query: INSERT INTO course_tutors (courseId, tutorId, isPrimary) SELECT 1, tp.userId, false FROM tutor_profiles tp INNER JOIN users u ON tp.userId = u.id WHERE tp.userId != (SELECT tutorId FROM course_tutors WHERE courseId = 1 AND isPrimary = true LIMIT 1) LIMIT 1
